trans-unit.source: Provides minimal design-time support for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Fornece suporte mínimo de tempo de design para <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"> </xref> controles.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartManagerDesigner class provides a bare-minimum design-time rendering of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control.
trans-unit.target: A classe WebPartManagerDesigner fornece um processamento de tempo de design mínimo bare do <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>controle.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: It appears on the design surface as a plain gray box showing the name of the class and the ID of the current <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>.
trans-unit.target: Ele aparece na superfície de design como uma caixa cinza simples mostrando o nome da classe e a ID da atual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: You can change the rendering of a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control by overriding the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> method in the same manner as with any standard <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>.
trans-unit.target: Você pode alterar o processamento de um personalizado <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>, substituindo o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A>método da mesma maneira como com qualquer <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> padrão</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> de controle</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> property is overridden to always return `true`.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>propriedade seja substituída para sempre retornar `true`.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Returns an empty string (""), which indicates that the visual design environment should revert to default control rendering.
trans-unit.target: Retorna uma cadeia de caracteres vazia (""), que indica que o ambiente de design visual deve ser revertida para o processamento de controle padrão.

trans-unit.source: Binds the designer to the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"></xref> control.
The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"></xref> control associated with the designer.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"> </xref> controle associado com o designer.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the designer should use a temporary copy rather than the actual control associated with the designer to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se o designer deve usar uma cópia temporária em vez do controle real associada com o designer para gerar a marcação de tempo de design.
